# Copy to `.cursor/mcp.env` (gitignored) and replace the placeholder.
#
# This is a Bugsnag *personal access token* for the Data Access API (MCP tools).
# It is NOT the same as the Flutter notifier key in photobooth/.env.
#
# Create one at: https://app.bugsnag.com → Settings → Organization settings → Access tokens
# Required permissions: Read projects, Read and write errors, Read and write comments
BUGSNAG_API_KEY=your-personal-access-token-here
